IT Security/Digital Forensics Sales Manager
29 Apr 2014 05:09 PM - UAE
.IT Security/Digital Forensics Sales ManagerT/TechnologyDubai, UAEPermanent
Updated April 21, 2014
The role will be reporting to the Head of Digital Forensics. Your responsibilities will be;• Identify new potential clients and ongoing regional business development for the organisation• Present the companies services to large multinational, local organisations and government• Follow up on sales opportunities with target clients and develop key relationships in the Middle East region• Travel within the Middle East region up to 30% of the time• Understands the company's Information Security and Digital Forensics offeringsWho we're looking for The ideal candidate will come from an Professional services/consultancy background and meet the below requirements:• 5-10 years experience including a minimum of 3 years in a business development role, and with a minimum of 3+ years working with IT Security/Digital Forensics role• Minimum requirement of a bachelor degree• Experience working for a multi-national company within the Middle East region• Candidates need to have experience selling to governmental and/or large multinational organisations• Candidates should already be based in the Middle East to be considered• Arabic language skills are preferred but not essentialHaving the following qualifications is also preferred; CCE / ACE / ENCE / GIH About our client A global leading technology company are looking to recruit a Sales Manager for the Digital Forensics team, based in Dubai working for leading IT/Technology company.What's on offer Highly attractive salary & benefits Cont (more...)
